title: How former players have returned to spark the Chiefs' perfect start
description: With an onslaught of injuries to starters, Andy Reid has been able to slide familiar faces into his lineup as if they never left.
author: Adam Teicher

title: Mayfield, Bucs looking to navigate 'critical game' vs. Chiefs without Godwin, Evans
description: Baker Mayfield is off to a hot start this season, but can the 4-4 Bucs keep their season afloat?

description: Lando Norris believes title rival Max Verstappen "got a bit lucky" with a rule "no one agrees with" in winning a dramatic Sao Paulo Grand Prix from 17th on the grid in a result that has left the McLaren driver's championship aspirations hanging by a thread.

title: Man Utd players want Van Nistelrooy to stay when Amorim takes charge
description: Manchester United players want Ruud van Nistelrooy to remain at the club when Ruben Amorim takes charge as their 'connector,' appreciating the way he has communicated with them.

title: I'm more grateful for each day - Sir Chris Hoy
description: Six-time Olympic gold medallist Sir Chris Hoy tells BBC Breakfast about his life with terminal cancer and the legacy he hopes to leave.

title: I'll never forget the words 'it's incurable' - Sir Chris Hoy on cancer diagnosis
description: Speaking to BBC Breakfast, Sir Chris Hoy says he "will never forget the words it's incurable" as he opens up about the moment he was diagnosed with stage four prostate cancer.

title: Spurs head coach Gregg Popovich reportedly out indefinitely after weekend health issue
